com.djdch.bukkit.util
Class Logger

java.lang.Object
  com.djdch.bukkit.util.Logger

public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object

Class who wrap the Minecraft Logger instance.

The purpose of this wrapper is to prefix each log message with the plugin name.

Author:
DjDCH
